300
00:22:41,790 --> 00:22:43,030
Young Master Fugui

301
00:22:43,510 --> 00:22:44,880
is amazing!

302
00:23:02,720 --> 00:23:03,830
Young Master Fugui,

303
00:23:03,830 --> 00:23:04,830
what do you think?

