306
00:23:07,720 --> 00:23:08,070
Oh.

307
00:23:18,880 --> 00:23:20,000
How strange.

308
00:23:20,960 --> 00:23:22,090
Young Master Fugui,

309
00:23:22,750 --> 00:23:25,350
