to release sword energy?

310
00:23:25,550 --> 00:23:26,880
It takes more practice.

311
00:23:29,000 --> 00:23:29,590
Okay.

312
00:23:50,200 --> 00:23:51,030
Young Master Fugui,

313
00:23:51,030 --> 00:23:51,790
look!

