00:23:52,160 --> 00:23:54,200
Such beautiful sunset glows.

315
00:23:57,030 --> 00:23:58,890
Young Master Fugui, look at that!

316
00:24:14,590 --> 00:24:15,720
They will disappear

317
00:24:17,310 --> 00:24:18,570
in just a short moment.

318
00:24:21,790 --> 00:24:23,920
