319
00:24:24,550 --> 00:24:26,200
What a pity.

320
00:24:34,590 --> 00:24:35,550
Young Master Fugui,

321
00:24:35,550 --> 00:24:36,510
look over there!

322
00:24:36,790 --> 00:24:37,790
A flock of birds!

323
00:24:47,440 --> 00:24:48,570
What a lovely scene.

324
00:24:54,550 --> 00:24:55,750
These birds

325
00:24:57,350 --> 00:24:59,080
came earlier today than usual.

326
00:25:03,480 --> 00:25:04,720
Young Master Fugui

327
00:25:05,160 --> 00:25:07,290
has never once seen the world outside.

328
00:25:08,680 --> 00:25:10,160
He'd even deeply cherish

329
00:25:10,590 --> 00:25:11,350
the presence

330
00:25:12,030 --> 00:25:13,750
of sunset glows and birds.

331
00:25:16,240 --> 00:25:18,840
Those people
confine Young Master Fugui here,

332
00:25:19,030 --> 00:25:20,830
making him cultivate every day.

333
00:25:21,000 --> 00:25:22,460
But he's a human after all.

