00:28:00,510 --> 00:28:01,840
I have a task to complete

378
00:28:01,960 --> 00:28:03,960
before leaving for the convention.

379
00:28:06,750 --> 00:28:08,310
A task?

380
00:28:12,270 --> 00:28:13,400
Young Master Fugui,

381
00:28:13,960 --> 00:28:14,680
may I...

382
00:28:15,750 --> 00:28:17,400
go with you?

383
00:28:30,720 --> 00:28:32,920
The Red Silver-ringed Snake Demon King

384
00:28:33,070 --> 00:28:34,070
likes clear water

385
00:28:34,070 --> 00:28:35,070
and dark forests.

386
