It once slaughtered
130 families in Kangshui Town.

387
00:28:38,830 --> 00:28:39,830
It's a killer and a looter

388
00:28:39,830 --> 00:28:41,000
that feeds on blood.

389
00:28:42,160 --> 00:28:44,750
Now, it is hiding in a valley
on Huyan Mountain.

390
00:28:44,750 --> 00:28:46,210
Yiqi Alliance has ordered

391
00:28:46,310 --> 00:28:47,310
to eliminate it.

392
00:29:33,310 --> 00:29:34,350
Soldier,

393
00:29:35,270 --> 00:29:38,670
you actually have the guts
to come alone and to try killing me.

394
00:29:39,030 --> 00:29:40,030
Today,

395
00:29:40,480 --> 00:29:42,440
I'm afraid you'll die here.

396
00:30:13,950 --> 00:30:15,920
[Snake Demon King]

397
00:30:46,000 --> 00:30:46,730
Who's there?

398
00:30:57,400 --> 00:30:58,310
Sir, help me.

399
00:30:58,830 --> 00:31:00,230
I'll share the treasures

400
00:31:00,720 --> 00:31:02,310
in my cave with you.

401
00:31:05,350 --> 00:31:07,350
You have a genuine dragon horn?

402
00:31:10,510 --> 00:31:12,640
He's drawing a talisman with dragon power.

403
00:31:12,640 --> 00:31:13,170
Soldier,

404
00:31:14,000 --> 00:31:14,930
you're done for!

405
00:32:13,440 --> 00:32:14,350
Sir,

406
00:32:14,880 --> 00:32:16,080
what happened to him?

407
00:32:16,640 --> 00:32:18,110
I've impaired his vision.

408
00:32:19,270 --> 00:32:20,930
You're a demon king after all.

409
00:32:21,920 --> 00:32:22,680
Don't tell me

410
00:32:24,160 --> 00:32:25,620
you can't beat a blind man.

411
00:32:26,310 --> 00:32:27,370
I'll leave the rest

412
00:32:27,510 --> 00:32:28,440
to you.

413
00:32:30,200 --> 00:32:30,880
Enjoy.

