00:33:20,510 --> 00:33:22,030
Who are you?

416
00:33:23,680 --> 00:33:24,510
I am...

417
00:33:25,480 --> 00:33:25,960
I...

418
00:33:30,110 --> 00:33:30,590
I...

419
00:33:31,240 --> 00:33:32,240
I don't fear you!

420
00:33:32,920 --> 00:33:34,320
Then why are you shaking?

421
00:33:34,960 --> 00:33:35,750
Because...

422
00:33:37,000 --> 00:33:38,460
B-Because you are a snake!

423
00:33:39,510 --> 00:33:41,310
My fellows and I all fear snakes.

424
00:33:42,790 --> 00:33:43,830
Then...

425
00:33:45,590 --> 00:33:47,250
why don't you get out of my way?

426
00:33:47,720 --> 00:33:48,160
I...

427
00:33:50,510 --> 00:33:52,440
I won't go away, though I'm scared!

428
00:33:57,440 --> 00:33:59,350
Inferior little thing...

429
00:34:01,270 --> 00:34:02,550
Go to hell!

430
00:34:03,510 --> 00:34:05,030
She's not a little thing,

431
00:34:06,240 --> 00:34:07,970
and she's by no means inferior!

432
00:34:32,250 --> 00:34:34,830
♪ I'm still impulsive like a youth ♪

433
00:34:35,150 --> 00:34:37,260
♪ I forget my sky-high ambition ♪

434
00:34:37,600 --> 00:34:43,020
♪ And the day it was dragged
into mud and dust ♪

435
00:34:43,710 --> 00:34:46,139
♪ If I can soar to great heights
with the wind as my ride  ♪

436
00:34:46,560 --> 00:34:48,820
♪ It must be you who keeps
the frost and snow out of my way ♪

437
00:34:49,489 --> 00:34:53,050
♪ And quietly sees me off ♪

438
00:34:57,280 --> 00:35:00,000
I didn't expect myself to behave so well
the first time I accompanied

439
00:35:00,000 --> 00:35:01,860
Young Master Fugui for a mission.

440
00:35:02,190 --> 00:35:03,630
Young Master Fugui, do you know

441
00:35:03,630 --> 00:35:05,440
that we spiders fear snakes most?

442
00:35:05,440 --> 00:35:06,239
I do know that.

443
00:35:06,630 --> 00:35:08,090
You've said it many times.

444
00:35:09,190 --> 00:35:09,989
Nonetheless,

445
00:35:10,190 --> 00:35:12,670
thanks to the sword skills you taught me,

446
00:35:13,360 --> 00:35:14,230
or a spider

447
00:35:14,550 --> 00:35:16,070
like me wouldn't dare to move at all

448
00:35:16,070 --> 00:35:17,670
in the face of a snake.

449
00:35:19,550 --> 00:35:20,550
It's true

450
00:35:21,510 --> 00:35:23,320
that I was terribly frightened

451
00:35:23,630 --> 00:35:24,550
the first time

452
00:35:24,550 --> 00:35:26,080
I went on a mission with you.

453
00:35:27,110 --> 00:35:28,280
But, Young Master Fugui,

454
00:35:28,280 --> 00:35:28,960
in general,

455
00:35:29,110 --> 00:35:30,800
I still did a good job, right?

456
00:35:30,960 --> 00:35:31,440
Yes.

457
00:35:35,710 --> 00:35:36,440
Candy?

458
00:35:38,960 --> 00:35:40,670
Is it a treat for me,

459
00:35:41,110 --> 00:35:42,240
Young Master Fugui?

460
00:35:43,670 --> 00:35:44,710
Thank you.

461
00:35:46,230 --> 00:35:46,920
Oh, right.

462
00:35:48,670 --> 00:35:49,550
Previously,

463
00:35:49,550 --> 00:35:51,030
I overheard a secret

464
00:35:51,030 --> 00:35:53,150
that Mr. Fei told Sword Attendant Shuang.

465
00:35:53,150 --> 00:35:54,810
I want to tell you about it now.

466
00:35:54,880 --> 00:35:56,740
I have something to say to you too.

467
00:35:57,280 --> 00:35:58,940
You have something to say too?

468
00:36:00,070 --> 00:36:00,670
Okay.

469
00:36:01,230 --> 00:36:02,230
You gave me candy.

470
00:36:02,280 --> 00:36:03,480
I'll let you go first.

