499
00:37:18,800 --> 00:37:19,280
Master,

500
00:37:19,920 --> 00:37:21,190
shall we set out

501
00:37:21,190 --> 00:37:22,790
for the Blue Sky Convention?

502
00:37:25,800 --> 00:37:27,200
Not after I visit a place.

503
00:37:28,760 --> 00:37:31,150
I need to find out
if that old guy Wangquan Shouyi

504
00:37:31,150 --> 00:37:32,400
has fulfilled

505
00:37:34,000 --> 00:37:35,150
his promise.

506
00:37:50,550 --> 00:37:52,710
This is a freshly made

507
00:37:52,920 --> 00:37:54,250
Dragon Tempering Pill.

508
00:37:58,840 --> 00:38:02,320
You claim your son Rumu to be able

509
00:38:02,320 --> 00:38:03,760
to slay the Soldier.

510
00:38:05,630 --> 00:38:06,490
Where is he now?

511
00:38:12,440 --> 00:38:14,070
