524
00:39:12,760 --> 00:39:14,440
You long to see the scenery outside,

525
00:39:14,440 --> 00:39:16,240
and to get out of that Palanquin.

526
00:39:16,360 --> 00:39:17,560
Mr. Fei said you could

527
00:39:17,590 --> 00:39:18,850
take a horse carriage,

528
00:39:19,070 --> 00:39:20,530
instead of the Palanquin,

529
00:39:20,800 --> 00:39:22,330
to the Blue Sky Convention.

530
00:39:22,800 --> 00:39:25,000
That way, you can see the world outside.

531
00:39:29,760 --> 00:39:31,020
Who would've known...

532
00:39:32,360 --> 00:39:34,490
