533
00:39:38,480 --> 00:39:39,550
How useless of me.

534
00:39:41,360 --> 00:39:42,690
I can't protect anyone.

535
00:39:50,030 --> 00:39:51,480
Why don't you be my eyes?

536
00:39:59,630 --> 00:40:02,670
Though Young Master Fugui
can't go outside as he pleases,

537
00:40:02,670 --> 00:40:03,510
I believe

538
00:40:03,880 --> 00:40:04,960
he will see

539
00:40:04,960 --> 00:40:07,560
the real Bamboo Pavilion by River Huai
one day,

