541
00:40:11,110 --> 00:40:12,150
Before that,

542
00:40:12,550 --> 00:40:13,510
if possible,

543
00:40:13,960 --> 00:40:16,710
I'd like to weave more prettier scenery

544
00:40:16,710 --> 00:40:18,040
for Young Master Fugui.

545
00:40:19,400 --> 00:40:20,230
Now, let me be

546
00:40:20,550 --> 00:40:22,590
Young Master Fugui's eyes.

547
00:40:47,550 --> 00:40:48,150
Sit tight.

548
00:40:54,880 --> 00:40:56,010
Young Master Fugui,

549
00:40:56,150 --> 00:40:57,000
yesterday,

